snippet.title: WarioWare DIY (DS) Media Summit Trailer
snippet.description: Nintendo Life - NINTENDO show us some more WarioWare action with Do It Yourself - create micro games on your Nintendo DS and then play them on Wii via WiiWare - More information at Nintendo Life
